(97, '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Mendhung kandel isih nggandhul ing langit Nopember. Mau bengi udan ngrejeh, gawe atise hawa esuk iki. Ing kana kene isih katon banyu ngecembong, prasasat ora ana maneh lemah garing. Ujian pungkasan gari rong sasi maneh, ujian kang bakal melu nemtokake dina ing tembe mburiku. Parandene rasane aku durung siyap babar pisan. Cathetan-cathetan ora komplit, buku-buku sing kudu daksinaoni semono uga. Atiku ngendhelong yen pinuju sinau bebarengan study club, sajake kanca-kancaluwih siyap. Ahh ya mbuh mengko!</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:36pt; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">(kapethik saka Panjebar Semngat 20/2008)</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:36pt; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Unsur intrinsik kang dipratelakake ing cerkak ing nduwur yaiku&hellip;.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li style=\"list-style-type:none\">\r\n	<ol style=\"list-style-type:lower-alpha\">\r\n		<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Alur</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n		<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Amanat</span></span