(140, '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Bathara kala</span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:36pt; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Bathara guru miyos siniwaka, dipunadhep Bathara Narada lan para Dewa. Ngrembang kawontenaning lelampahan lan papesthening dumadi. Boten watawis dangu katungka sowanipun Bathara Kala. Nyuwun papancaning tedhanipun. Bathara Kala dipunparengaken nedha golongannipun sato kewan, sarta ugi manungsa, ingkang nandhang lepating dumadi ing antawisipun inggih punika: Ontang-anting, Dhampit, Sekar Sepasang, Uger-uger Lawang, Sendhang Kapit Pancuran, Pandhawa lima, Sraimpi, lsp.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:36pt; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Lare kang lair sareng sadinten, jaler kaliyan estri inggih punika&hellip;.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li style=\"list-style-type:none\">\r\n	<ol style=\"list-style-type:lower-alpha\">\r\n		<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Kedhana-kedhini</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n		<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Pandhawa lima</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n